  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t看了yahoo map上，中华西太后的评语，觉得相当有意思。<br/>\r\nhttps://loco.yahoo.co.jp/place/g-FcJFDuS8OD6/review/?bm=ymap_poi_photo_more<br/>\n<br/>\r\n日本人的评语相当温和而克制，最严厉的顶多就是:「我开始讨厌中国人了」，你看不到<mark>支那</mark>贱畜这种极端的词。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n现代的日本人普遍温和有礼。那些宣扬反日情绪的人，真的该去死一死。日本早就不是八十年前那个军国主义国家了。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n以下机翻成中文:<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTRlOTMzODIzMTU0ZTY2OGExMTY4LmpwZz93aWR0aD05MzImaGVpZ2h0PTE3NTQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4e933823154e668a1168.jpg?width=932&amp;height=1754\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4e933823154e668a1168.jpg?width=932&amp;height=1754\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a4e933823154e668a1168.jpg?width=932&amp;height=1754\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGFkNWRlMTM2MTYwZDY1MGU2Mzk3LmpwZz93aWR0aD05MzMmaGVpZ2h0PTE3NTU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dad5de136160d650e6397.jpg?width=933&amp;height=1755\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dad5de136160d650e6397.jpg?width=933&amp;height=1755\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dad5de136160d650e6397.jpg?width=933&amp;height=1755\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWViMTkwZDExZGUzZmYzNDczNGJmLmpwZz93aWR0aD05MzcmaGVpZ2h0PTE3NDY\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5eb190d11de3ff34734bf.jpg?width=937&amp;height=1746\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5eb190d11de3ff34734bf.jpg?width=937&amp;height=1746\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5eb190d11de3ff34734bf.jpg?width=937&amp;height=1746\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGRhYzY4NTY5NTAxODkxODY2MWI5LmpwZz93aWR0